AI Image Detector is a tool that helps you quickly verify whether an image was generated by artificial intelligence. It adds a new action to the browser's context menu, allowing you to analyze images directly from the browser. Once an image is selected, the extension uses the Sightengine API to determine the likelihood that the image was AI-generated, and returns a percentage-based result.

Key Features:

Analyze images with one click from the context menu
Quick percentage-based results
Works with any image displayed in the browser
